name: FlockDesign - Private Island Short
description:
18g (regular earlobe holes)

These earrings were hand cut in the USA using leather previously sourced for Rodeo Chaps. They may also contain leather from a company that manufactures accordians, or the trim leather from an upholstery shop. So throw them on, ride a bull, play a tune, and redesign your house. These earrings have history.

Wear them well, wear them out. As you wear your new Flocks earrings, they will "bloom". To make them new again, simply press in a dictionary over night.

Flock Design by Kathryn Greenwood Swanson.
